    "lyrics": {
      "text": "As one val-iant in mar--tyr--dom,___ tro-phy-bear--er, Great Mar-tyr__ George, on this day__ we gath--er__ to___ chant thee hymns of__ praise;__ for thou hast__ fin---ished the course and__ hast____ in-vin-ci-bly kept__ the Faith,____ and from__ God thou__ hast___ re-ceived thy great vic--to-ry’s crown of__ light;__ hence en--treat the__ Lord to de-liv-er__ from__ per-ils and__ cor--rup---tion____ them that__ faith-ful--ly do__ hon---our thine ev-er-ven---’ra--ble mem-o--ry.__"
    }
  }
